title: #130 - Did Lil Nas X Steal Old Town Road?
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we (maybe) EXPOSE lil nas X, who just this week became the record holder for longest at #1 on Billboard, as a song THIEF and possible incarnation of the devil himself. We also talk about nude leaks, licking icecream, Faceapp, and a whooooole lot more!
